title: #689 - Cory n Chad The Smash Brothers
description:
Cory n Chad, are identical twin brothers and stand up comedians known as The Smash Brothers. You have seen them on Showtime and Fox. Today they join Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio.
